  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "Firefly Foundry built this alongside the Ranger as one of their first two designs, exclusively for Riley's Rangers. Three standard variants right out of the gate, each covering a different range bracket, and two more later on. The sixth variant, the ND-RRDS, is the odd one out, built in 3102 specifically to mark the partnership between the Rangers and Clan Sea Fox. That one also saw service with the Sea Foxes themselves, which tells you something about what the partnership was worth to both sides.",
